OL,3,CAir conditioning units sell out at
OL,4,CLidl store amid long queues
OL,6,FThere were long queues for air-
OL,7,Fconditioning units at a Hampshire
OL,8,Fsupermarket this morning as extreme
OL,9,Fheat continued to impact much of the
OL,10,Farea.
OL,12,FCustomers waited in line at Lidl in
OL,13,FHedge End on Thursday morning (25
OL,14,FJune) but were told that the items had
OL,15,Fsold out.
OL,17,FIt comes the day after temperatures in
OL,18,FGosport reached 36.1 degrees, with a
OL,19,Freading of 35.8 recorded in
OL,20,FWiggonholt, West Sussex
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
