OL,3,CAir conditioning units sell out at
OL,4,CLidl store amid long queues
OL,6,FNetwork Rail have advised passengers
OL,7,Fto only travel if "absolutely
OL,8,Fnecessary" on Thursday and Friday.
OL,10,FThe Met Office said that the
OL,11,Fexceptional heat will spread
OL,12,Fnorthwards on Thursday, "with an even
OL,13,Fhotter day ahead for some with amber
OL,14,Fand red extreme heat warnings in
OL,15,Fforce".
OL,17,FHowever some places might feel
OL,18,Fslightly cooler due to a brisk breeze
OL,19,Fin the south, it said.
